text: Map of Russia with Chelyabinsk Oblast highlighted This is a list of rural localities in Chelyabinsk Oblast. Chelyabinsk Oblast (, Chelyabinskaya oblast) is a federal subject (an oblast) of Russia in the Ural Mountains region, on the border of Europe and Asia. Its administrative center is the city of Chelyabinsk.
